title: PAIGE Men's Doheny Relaxed Straight in Heritage Jeans
description: The Doheny is a heritage PAIGE fit that we’re excited to breathe new life into. This relaxed straight leg silhouette is crafted from our PAIGE Heritage denim in a light stone wash with natural fading, tacking details at the waistband, and a slight tint for a vintage vibe. Our Heritage denim offers the same vintage-inspired character while maintaining the soft hand-feel and comfort you’ve come to love and expect from PAIGE.
